ModRefiner performs all-atom reconstruction from the C-alpha trace.
After backbone reconstruction, ModRefiner optimizes the backbone H-bond network. Side chain reconstruction is followed by additional optimization with a composite physicsand knowledge- based force field.
NCN performs side chain reconstruction from the protein backbone.
Uses optimized OPLS parameters, simulated-annealing search strategy and a detailed rotamer library.
Opus_Rota performs side chain reconstruction from the protein backbone.
