assembly, (3) elongation by dock-lock monomer addition, and (4) growth by dock-lock oligomer addition. The lower panel highlights the capabilities of all-atom approaches limited to the forming of small oligomers or the short-scale dynamics of formed aggregates. The “Under Construction” sign emphasize the inaccessibility of the intermediate aggregation stages to all-atom modeling. Adapted from ref.31 Copyright 2014
